  "texts": [
    "By systematically cleaning and transforming the raw email data, we enhance the ability of the detection models to learn meaningful patterns and relationships, thereby improving their accuracy and effectiveness in identifying spam messages.",
    "C. Evaluation MetricsThe performance of ChatGPT-4 and Google Gemini in spam detection was rigorously evaluated using a set of standard metrics, ensuring a comprehensive assessment of their capabilities.",
    "These metrics are essential for understanding different aspects of model performance, including their ability to correctly identify spam and legitimate emails, as well as their effectiveness in balancing the trade-offs between various types of errors.",
    "The following metrics were employed:• Accuracy: Defined as the proportion of total predictions (spam and ham) that were correct.",
    "Mathematically, it is expressed as:Accuracy = True Positives +True Negatives Total Number of Predictions, where True Positives (TP) are spam emails correctly identified as spam, and True Negatives (TN) are legitimate emails correctly identified as not spam."
  ],
